    <title>Cost of War Act of 2015</title>
    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2015-06-30T19:03:18Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Cost of War Act of 2015 </strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Defense (DOD), in consultation with the Internal Revenue Service, to post on the DOD public website, the cost to each U.S. taxpayer of each of the wars in Afghanistan, Iraq, and Syria. </p>]]></text>
